OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FThe mother of a vulnerable teenager
OL,7,Fwith a history of self-harm believes
OL,8,Fher daughter would still be alive if
OL,9,Fshe'd received the 'correct care'.
OL,11,FCariss Stone died aged 19 in August
OL,12,F2019, two days after being found on a
OL,13,Fbathroom floor at a psychiatric
OL,14,Fintensive care unit having attempted
OL,15,Fto take her own life.
OL,17,F, Somerset NHS Foundation Trust said
OL,18,Fthe teenager, who was from, could
OL,19,F"possibly" have been saved if she had
OL,20,Fbeen more frequently monitored.
