OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FThe former Strode College student was
OL,7,Fjudged a high enough risk to herself
OL,8,Fto need welfare checks several times
OL,9,Fan hour at the psychiatric intensive
OL,10,Fcare unit where she spent the final
OL,11,Ftwo months of her life.
OL,13,F"Had Cariss' care been managed
OL,14,Fdifferently, we think she would still
OL,15,Fbe with us and working towards her
OL,16,Fhopes and dreams for the future," said
OL,17,Fher mother, Gina Schiraldi.
