OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,F"We miss Cariss very much. There is a
OL,7,Fspace where she should be ` she is
OL,8,Fmissing from family photos, and there
OL,9,Fis an empty chair where she should be
OL,10,Fsat at the dinner table. There is only
OL,11,Fsilence where there should be music
OL,12,Fand laughter, enjoying time and making
OL,13,Fplans with friends and family."
OL,15,FDr Lucy Knight, Medical Director of
OL,16,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust, told
OL,17,Fthe jury at Wells Town Hall that there
OL,18,Fwas confusion among staff as to how
OL,19,Foften Cariss needed monitored.
