OL,3,CMore checks could 'possibly' have
OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,FDr Knight said the sheets were
OL,7,F"totally unhelpful and misleading"
OL,8,Fbecause they resulted in staff filling
OL,9,Fin records that weren't true.
OL,11,FCCTV footage from the day Cariss was
OL,12,Ffound in the bathroom shows that some
OL,13,Fof her checks were up to 12 minutes
OL,14,Fapart.
OL,16,FUnder questioning from solicitor
OL,17,FScarlett Milligan, on behalf of
OL,18,FCariss's family, Dr Knight conceded
OL,19,Fthat had Cariss actually been
OL,20,Fmonitored every five minutes her life
OL,21,Fmight "possibly" have been saved.
