OL,6,FShe added that she believed a five-
OL,7,Fminute regime was unrealistic and
OL,8,Fcould cause extra stress to
OL,9,Fpsychiatric patients.
OL,11,FThe inquest previously heard how
OL,12,FCariss had struggled with anorexia and
OL,13,Fself harm since she was 14.
