OL,6,FJane Yeandle, service group director
OL,7,Ffor mental health and learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities at SomersetJNHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust said: "Our deepest
OL,10,Fsympathies go out to Cariss' family
OL,11,Ffor their tragic loss. We apologise
OL,12,Fwholeheartedly for the shortcomings in
OL,13,Fthe care we provided.
OL,15,F"We accept the coroner's findings and
OL,16,Fwill act on those recommendations.
