OL,6,F"In 2019 we commissioned an external
OL,7,Freview, which touched on some of the
OL,8,FthemesJdiscussed at the inquest and
OL,9,Fmade a number of improvements to our
OL,10,Fsystems andJprocesses to ensure we are
OL,11,Fworking in line with best practice. We
OL,12,Fwill look closely at theJcoroner's
OL,13,Ffinding to see whether there's more we
OL,14,Fcan do.
