OL,4,Csaved teenager's life - NHS trust
OL,6,F"We have improved the training for
OL,7,Fcolleagues who undertake clinical
OL,8,Fobservations, toJensure all details
OL,9,Fare clearly recorded and that
OL,10,Fcolleagues communicate more
OL,11,FeffectivelyJwith each other. We will
OL,12,Falso undertake to improve the way we
OL,13,Finvolve and communicateJwith families
OL,14,Fduring the investigation of incidents."
